snippet.title: Lets Play Pokemon Dark Rising - Part 1 : A New Journey Begins
snippet.description:
MrsExile Plays the new Pokemon Hack Dark Rising

On this new Journey MExile sets out to defeat the Core League, however there are bigger plans on the horizon for her, ones that will change the Pokemon world as we know it....
